Volunteer Registration
вЂ‹Focus on availability, skills, and contact information so the NGO can match them with the right events.
вЂ‹Full Name
вЂ‹Email Address & Phone Number
вЂ‹Date of Birth (To verify age for certain tasks)
вЂ‹Skills/Interests (e.g., Teaching, Event Planning, Social Media, Manual Labor)
вЂ‹Availability (Dropdown: Weekends, Weekdays, or specific hours)
вЂ‹Emergency Contact Info
вЂ‹Location (City/Neighborhood)
вЂ‹2. Donor Registration
вЂ‹This form should be the shortest to reduce "friction" and encourage contributions. Keep it focused on identity and communication.
вЂ‹Full Name (or Organization Name)
вЂ‹Email Address (For sending tax-deductible receipts)
вЂ‹Phone Number (Optional)
вЂ‹Mailing Address (Required if sending physical receipts or thank-you kits)
вЂ‹Tax ID / PAN Number (Often required by law for tax exemption certificates)
вЂ‹Preferred Causes (Checkbox list: Education, Health, Environment, etc.)
вЂ‹3. NGO Partner Registration
вЂ‹This is a Business-to-Business (B2B) style form. You need to verify their legitimacy before allowing them to collect funds or post events.
вЂ‹Organization Name
вЂ‹NGO Registration Number / License Info
вЂ‹Contact Person Name & Title
вЂ‹Official Email & Website URL
вЂ‹Organization Address
вЂ‹Mission Statement (Short bio of what they do)
вЂ‹Bank Account Details (Crucial for fund disbursement)
вЂ‹Verification Documents (File upload for legal certificates)
вЂ‹4. Admin Registration
вЂ‹Typically, Admins aren't registered through a public form for security reasons. However, if you are building an internal setup:
вЂ‹Full Name
вЂ‹Work Email
вЂ‹Employee ID / Internal Reference
вЂ‹Role Level (Dropdown: Super Admin, Moderator, Financial Reviewer)
вЂ‹Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) Setup (Highly recommended for this role)
вЂ‹Key Technical Recommendations
вЂ‹Privacy & Security: Ensure you have a Terms & Conditions and Privacy Policy checkbox on every form, especially since you are handling sensitive donor and legal data.
вЂ‹Validation: Use real-time validation for email formats and phone numbers to prevent "junk" signups.
вЂ‹Social Sign-in: Consider adding "Sign up with Google" for Volunteers and Donors to speed up the process.
